snippet.title: Söldner-X 2: Final Prototype - The Last Chapter trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.soldner-x.com - Check out Söldner-X 2: Final Prototype - The Last Chapter's official launch trailer, hitting the PlayStation®Network in November 2010.

This expansion pack adds three brand new and exciting stages, 13 diverse new challenges, 11 new trophies and a few more surprises to the original game.

For more information, visit http://www.soldner-x.com
